<br>
What I seek is knowledge.  I wanted to hear from the guys and gals that have been on the receiving end of my heal spells the past 65 levels and can tell me some things I want to know.<br>
<br>
1.  Please take a moment to look at the Magelo for Snapricot.  Is there anything that seems grossly out of place or should be upgraded for a warrior at her level?<br>
<br>
2.  Could someone explain to me the mainhand/offhand philosophy and what makes a good combo?  I was told that I should get a fast, preferably proc'ing weapon for main, then a slower, heavier-hitting weapon for offhand.  Why is that?<br>
<br>
