<br>
4.  Breaking mezzes.  I was told to taunt 2x, then break, but then sometimes I am told the opposite.  Is there a general rule of thumb regarding this?<br>
<br>
5.  Regarding /shield, I know it protects the target, i.e. &quot;Jullianna begins to use Snapricot as a living shield&quot; but when shielded, what does that do?<br>
<br>
That is all I can think of right now.  More will come as I think of them.  Thanks for your assistance in advance. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
