<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>1. Please take a moment to look at the Magelo for Snapricot. Is there anything that seems grossly out of place or should be upgraded for a warrior at her level? <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
