<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>4. Breaking mezzes. I was told to taunt 2x, then break, but then sometimes I am told the opposite. Is there a general rule of thumb regarding this?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
